summary: I am an energetic, self-motivated professional with a keen interest in contributing positively to our world. I have lived, worked and studied in ten countries and speak various languages. As such, I am highly adaptable, a quick learner, and a strong intercultural communicator. Always eager for new challenges, I  have experience in working with stakeholders from a variety of cultures, backgrounds, and sectors and possess well-developed writing, presentation, and critical thinking skills.
